1. Get a bootanimation.zip e.g. from http://androidbootanimation.com or create it by your own (name must be bootanimation.zip, for the structure orient on the original or one from that site...)
2. Use an Filebrowser with root access on your phone. Change to the folder /system/media
3. Rename the existing bootanimation.zip to e.g. bootanimation.zip.bak
4. Copy the new bootanimation.zip to /system/media/bootanimation.zip
